{
  "id": "adv_main_03_03_01",
  "title": "BIG4編1章11話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_meeting-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_01-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "BIG4に……どりきゅんに、私達が挑戦……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "To the BIG4… to DoriKyun‚ we'll challenge…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_01-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "詳しく聞かせてもらえますか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Can you tell us more about it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、順番に説明するよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ I'll explain everything in order.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "BIG4はアイドル界の頂点に君臨している\nそれ以外のアイドルとは明確な壁がある存在なんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The BIG4 reigns at the top of the idol world.\nThey are a presence with a clear wall between them and all other idols.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_01-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "だからこそ、それ以外のアイドルがBIG4に\n挑戦することは、基本的には不可能なんですわよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's why it's basically impossible for any other idol\nto challenge the BIG4.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.0447163423,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_01-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "チャンスがあるとすれば、大きな大会……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If there’s a chance‚ it would be in a big tournament…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_01-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "I-UNITYや、二年に一度の\nVENUSグランプリみたいに本当に大規模な大会よね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Like I-UNITY or the VENUS Grand Prix that happens\nonce every two years‚ a really large-scale tournament.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.9461905686,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "そんな状況の中、どりきゅんの復活記念として\nBIG4チャレンジの企画が持ち上がったらしい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In such a situation‚ it seems like a plan for a BIG4 Challenge\nhas come up as part of DoriKyun's comeback celebration.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "彼女達に一度でも勝てれば、BIG4の座を\n手に入れられるという……異例も異例の企画なんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you can beat them even once‚ you can take their place\nin the BIG4… It's an unusual plan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_01-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "わー、なんかすっごい盛り上がりそうだね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wow‚ it sounds like it's going to be really exciting!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "そうなんだ。負けて元々だし勝てればBIG4入り……\nそんな状況だから、応募が殺到してるみたいだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It is. There's nothing to lose and becomimg BIG4 if we win…\nIn that kind of situation‚ it seems like applications are flooding in.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_01-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "……なんだか妙な話ですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…That sounds strange.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_trouble-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 67.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_01-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "沙季？　どうしましたの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Saki? What’s wrong?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_01-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "どりきゅんの活動再開を盛り上げるための\nイベントだということは分かります",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I understand that it’s an event\nto promote DoriKyun’s comeback.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.4082519224,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_01-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "ですが、勝つのが当然で、負ければ今の地位を失う",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But for them to risk their position if they lose‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_01-ski005.m4a",
      "text": "BIG4でもナンバー3の超大物の行動にしては……\nあまりにも割に合わないんじゃないでしょうか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "for a big shot like them‚ the number three in the BIG4…\nIsn’t it a little too much of a gamble?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "うーん、その点は確かに謎なんだよな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm‚ that's certainly a mystery…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_01-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "それだけ自信があるってことじゃない？\n「ふはははー！　かかってこーい！」って感じなのかも",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Maybe they’re just that confident?\nMaybe they’re like‚ \"Fuhahahaha! Come and get me!\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_01-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "アイドルにそんな大魔王みたいな人はいませんわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There’s no idol who’s like a demon king.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_01-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "でも、貴重なチャンスなのは間違いないですよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But it’s definitely a valuable chance‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "そうだな。本来、BIG4の入れかわりは数年に一度\nあるかどうかの、極めて大きな出来事なんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re right. Normally‚ a change in the BIG4 happens\nonly once every few years‚ if at all. It’s a huge deal.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.8230055535,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "サニピとスリクスが入れかわって間もなく\nこんな機会が訪れるのは稀……どころか、俺も初めてだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s rare for such an opportunity to come up\nso soon after Sunny Peace and IIIX switched places… In fact‚ this is my first time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_01-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんは……今の私達が\nどりきゅんに勝てると思いますか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san… do you think we\ncan beat DoriKyun now?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_pop-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 129.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "ああ。月ストはI-UNITY以来、ずっと地道に\n努力を続けて、確実に力をつけている",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. Moon Tempest has been working hard steadily\nsince I-UNITY and has definitely gotten stronger.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "先日の野外フェス……IMFだって、スリクスに話題を\n持っていかれはしたが……ステージは素晴らしかった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The other day at the outdoor festival… the IMF‚ even though IIIX\nstole the show… your stage was amazing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_01-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "そうですわ！　私を褒めたたえるコメントも\n沢山ありましてよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s right! There were a lot of\ncomments praising me!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 148.3000001001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_01-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "すずにゃん、フェスが終わってからも\nずーっと検索してたもんね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Suzu-nyan‚ you were searching for them\neven after the festival ended.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 152.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "相手はBIG4の一角だ。勝てるとは断言出来ない\nそれでも……今の月ストなら、勝ち目は十分にある",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Our opponent is one of the BIG4. I can't say for sure that we can win.\nBut… with Moon Tempest as it is now‚ we have a good chance.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 160.0333334334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_01-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "勝てなかったとしても確実に成長に繋がるし\n挑戦する価値はあると思うんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even if we don’t win‚ it will definitely lead to our growth‚\nand I think it’s worth the challenge.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 168.4333334334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_01-ktn004.m4a",
